href="erct-003K.xml"
title="Embedding"
addr="erct-003K"
type="local">embeddings</fr:link>) respectively. It is common to refer to a <fr:em>full</fr:em> and <fr:em>faithful</fr:em> functor as <fr:em><fr:strong>fully faithful</fr:strong></fr:em>.</fr:p><fr:p>Fullness and faithfulness are both <fr:em><fr:link
href="erct-001I.xml"
title="Proposition"
addr="erct-001I"
type="local">properties</fr:link></fr:em> of a functor.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree><fr:tree
